metadata.name: JEWELED Magritte's Sky
metadata.description:
Welcome to the enchanting world of JEWELED, where together we redefine the boundaries of traditional jewelry craftsmanship with AI.

JEWELED Magritte's Sky is exclusively created for the AI Surrealism exhibition at Oculus NYC, hosted by Superchief Gallery NFT and Exquisite Workers. The largest AI art show in history, featuring 100 AI artists, on June 2-8, 2023, is curated by Anna Dart and Roger Haus.
